---
import Container from "../../primitives/Container.astro";
---
<section class="section-pad bg-white" aria-labelledby="our-story-title">
  <Container>
    <div class="grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-[1.03fr_0.97fr] lg:gap-14 lg:items-stretch">

      <!-- Left: Story text -->
      <div class="reveal max-w-[38rem] lg:py-1">
        <p class="eyebrow">Our Story</p>
        <h2 id="our-story-title" class="fluid-h2 mt-3 max-w-[13ch] text-balance">
          Together We Can Make a Difference
        </h2>
        <p class="fluid-lead mt-6 text-muted">
          Empereal was founded to help rapidly growing economies manage one of their most critical infrastructure challenges: the widening gap between demand and supply in energy and fresh water. Our services are built to be innovative and reliable, enabling clients to meet their growing needs sustainably and cost-effectively.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-5 text-muted leading-relaxed">
          Since 2008, Empereal and its partners have driven the development, fabrication, and testing of solar-powered solutions worldwide. We aim to create lasting social impact — improving quality of life and sustainability for industrial, commercial, and rural communities alike. Our expertise spans the full project lifecycle, allowing us to design, build, and operate renewable energy solutions tailored to any requirement.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-5 text-muted leading-relaxed">
          Headquartered in Singapore, Empereal operates across India, the Middle East, and the USA.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Mission + Vision cards -->
      <div class="grid grid-rows-2 gap-5 reveal h-full">
        <!-- Vision -->
        <div class="relative flex min-h-0 flex-col justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-primary-dark p-7 lg:p-8 ring-1 ring-accent/20">
          <div class="absolute -top-8 -right-8 h-32 w-32 rounded-full bg-accent/10 blur-2xl" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-5">
            <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center h-9 w-9 rounded-lg bg-accent/20 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" class="h-4 w-4 text-accent" fill="none">
                <path d="M10 2a8 8 0 100 16A8 8 0 0010 2zm0 3a1 1 0 011 1v4l2.5 2.5a1 1 0 01-1.414 1.414L9.5 11.414A1 1 0 019 10.5V6a1 1 0 011-1z" fill="currentColor"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
            <h3 class="font-display text-sm font-semibold text-accent tracking-wide uppercase">Vision</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-white/80 leading-7">
            Empereal Energy and Services aims to be the provider of choice for renewable energy and desalinated water in growing economies — delivering solutions that significantly reduce environmental footprint and improve sustainability for industries and commercial establishments.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Mission -->
        <div class="relative flex min-h-0 flex-col justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-surface border border-primary/10 p-7 lg:p-8 ring-1 ring-primary/10">
          <div class="absolute -bottom-8 -left-8 h-32 w-32 rounded-full bg-accent/8 blur-2xl" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-5">
            <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center h-9 w-9 rounded-lg bg-accent/15 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" class="h-4 w-4 text-accent-dark" fill="none">
                <path d="M10 3.5a6.5 6.5 0 100 13 6.5 6.5 0 000-13zM2 10a8 8 0 1116 0A8 8 0 012 10zm8-3a1 1 0 011 1v2.586l1.707 1.707a1 1 0 01-1.414 1.414l-2-2A1 1 0 019 11V8a1 1 0 011-1z" fill="currentColor"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
            <h3 class="font-display text-sm font-semibold text-primary-dark tracking-wide uppercase">Mission</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-ink leading-7">
            Empereal empowers communities through the delivery of clean energy, pure water, and green hydrogen, using innovative and cost-effective technologies. With 18+ years of experience across multiple regions, we contribute to social projects that improve quality of life for industrial, commercial, and rural communities.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </Container>
</section>
